{"tid":931120,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔講咁多 總知以後大家唔好再幫襯瘋宅","createTime":"2018-12-06T21:51:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T23:26:04.000Z","uid":6783,"like":25,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"79170ab6b79a758504cf26102e6ff872ec42e006","tid":931120,"uid":6783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T21:51:16.000Z","msg":"除左呢單野之外 本身瘋宅個價就貴過人<br />\n質素又差過人<br />\n全行都知瘋宅sales真係最廢嫁啦<br />\n無料又串！<br />\n百記so寧個d服務好又平d<br />\n連賣緊既貨都新d同前衛d<br />\n瘋宅既死板態度同價貴呢樣野本身都無乜人買<br />\n<br />\n做過瘋宅都知 標價賣貨已經低佣金 <br />\n仲要放埋d AC886 VL999出去 變0佣都算 當跑大數<br />\n問題係放埋呢個價都唔夠人平啊你老母！<br />\n<br />\n呢間公司對客又當你狗咁撚<br />\n對同事又當你乞衣咁比佣金<br />\n<br />\n一齊抵制佢啦！"},{"pid":"10f6993ad48fb7d1cf611d87151e7f92adad643a","tid":931120,"uid":219614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T21:53:09.000Z","msg":"今次你有訂嗎"},{"pid":"f50d2076b73a523dde58fe368e5920773f03a8f3","tid":931120,"uid":6783,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"10f6993ad48fb7d1cf611d87151e7f92adad643a","tid":931120,"uid":219614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T21:53:09.000Z","msg":"今次你有訂嗎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T21:54:25.000Z","msg":"無 利申 做左好耐瘋宅 今年先無做"},{"pid":"5da0cbba512bce9d888a7e8b8b80fdc3ab05cd16","tid":931120,"uid":219614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T21:55:33.000Z","msg":"一向係百老匯買，但呢幾年都好少係電器鋪買野"},{"pid":"297b29a3df218303b63efea6389d9eeb04dcc73d","tid":931120,"uid":6783,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"5da0cbba512bce9d888a7e8b8b80fdc3ab05cd16","tid":931120,"uid":219614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T21:55:33.000Z","msg":"一向係百老匯買，但呢幾年都好少係電器鋪買野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T21:58:33.000Z","msg":"百記起碼真係有d潮野比你揀下<br />\n例如Ironman 侏羅紀放濕機 有錶<br />\n瘋宅得個d淘寶野都算 仲要賣$299?"},{"pid":"d1af5eabe74c433472876a4440f58a389657c9fb","tid":931120,"uid":219614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T22:00:03.000Z","msg":"